{"tid":1912189,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Naughty Dog宣布將與HBO合作推出《The Last of Us》電視劇","createTime":"2020-03-06T01:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T05:26:08.000Z","uid":75050,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f5c33242026fe2839757f7914ea1acf3c1ebe71","tid":1912189,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GLXUnHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGLXUnHA.jpg&h=2a30cb82&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNaughty Dog宣布將與HBO合作推出《The Last of Us》電視劇，Naughty Dog創意總監Neil Druckmann和美劇《Chernobyl》編劇Craig Mazin將共同擔任導演和編劇。曾創作《The Sopranos》《Sex and the City》等劇的Carolyn Strauss和Naughty Dog總裁Evan Wells也將出任本劇的執行制作人。<br />\n<br />\n這將是PlayStation Productions推出的第一部電視劇，主要呈現《The Last of Us 1》的故事，但也有可能加入《The Last of Us 二部曲》的相關內容。IGN表示本劇將取代之前的《The Last of Us》電影項目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEqVRAW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEqVRAW.jpg&h=075070d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78287ccf6e98fec0ed2c142b5eeb04e972b7d12e","tid":1912189,"uid":90749,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/logan-film-review.jpg?w=780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Flogan-film-review.jpg%3Fw%3D780&h=ad1d453c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"680bb4925003befe7ff2a38def80ea60aa7bf499","tid":1912189,"uid":78773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"78287ccf6e98fec0ed2c142b5eeb04e972b7d12e","tid":1912189,"uid":90749,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.indiewire.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/logan-film-review.jpg?w=780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2